        Create and store a new mapping set in the DB.
        Parameters:
        mappingName - - The name of the mapping set (used for the FSN and preferred term of the underlying concept)
        inverseName - - (optional) inverse name of the mapping set (if it makes sense for the mapping)
        purpose - - (optional) - user specified purpose of the mapping set
        description - - the intended use of the mapping set
        editorStatus - - (optional) user specified status concept of the mapping set
